                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable R</hi> 139.) I took the prisoner—he said, "It is done, and it can't be helped."</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> When I turned out it was under my hammock; and it is a rule when anything is found to take it to the captain, but we cannot see him till nine o'clock.</p>
